``inf`` is missing from Python's builtins. This module adds it:



..

  import inf

  # inf is now float("+inf")



  inf.div(10.0, 0.0)  # Correctly returns inf.







CHANGELOG

---------



2013-10-21 Release 1.1.0

    Added the ``inf.div`` function for IEEE division.



